%N A275905 Expansion of (1-x-2*x^2) / (1-6*x+3*x^2-2*x^3).
%C A275905 Number of maximal matchings in the hexagonal snake graph on 5*n + 1 vertices with cut vertices at distance 2. - _Andrew Howroyd_, Jul 19 2026
%H A275905 Colin Barker, <a href="/A275905/b275905.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
