%H A275905 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (6,-3,2).
%F A275905 a(n) = 6*a(n-1)-3*a(n-2)+2*a(n-3) for n>2. - _Colin Barker_, Aug 26 2016
